      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">4.1403</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d286e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d288e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Except as provided in paragraph (b) of this section, the contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.204-10.dita#FAR_52_204_10"
                        base="i1064087"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-10</xref>, Reporting Executive Compensation and First-Tier Subcontract Awards, in all solicitations and contracts of <ph rev="FAC 2025-06 October 1, 2025" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2024-001?>$40,000<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 4.1403 in paragraph (a) by removing “$30,000” and adding “$40,000” in its place.?></ph> or more.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d288e18">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The clause is not prescribed for contracts that are not required to be reported in the Federal Procurement Data System (FPDS) (see <xref href="Subpart_4.6.dita#FAR_Subpart_4_6"
                        base="i1122770"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  4.6</xref>).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
